Additional Notes:

This project is a unique implementation of falling-block puzzle mechanics
featuring:
- Original 20×20 grid design (expanded from traditional 10×20)
- Custom mobile-optimized invisible gesture controls
- Strict monochrome visual design philosophy
- Battery-efficient rendering optimizations
- Cross-platform responsive design

The core falling-block puzzle gameplay mechanics are not subject to copyright
and are widely implemented across the gaming community. This implementation
contains no copyrighted code from other sources.

Third-party resources used:
- Google Fonts: Electrolize (licensed under SIL Open Font License)
- HTML5 Canvas API (web standard)
- CSS3 specifications (web standard)
- JavaScript ES6+ features (web standard)

For questions about licensing or usage, please refer to the MIT License terms
above or contact the project maintainers through GitHub issues.